 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Hi-C Diff\n",
    "\n",
    "Draw the difference between two Hi-C contact matrices."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import coolbox\n",
    "from coolbox.api import *"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": true
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": "'0.3.0'"
     },
     "execution_count": 2,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "coolbox.__version__"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_dir = \"../../../tests/test_data/\"\n",
    "cl1 = f\"{data_dir}/cool_chr1_89000000_90400000_for_cmp_1.mcool\"\n",
    "cl2 = f\"{data_dir}/cool_chr1_89000000_90400000_for_cmp_2.mcool\"\n",
    "\n",
    "region = \"chr1:89237500-90227500\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Normalize with `expect` matrix (decay along diagonal), difference with `diff` (matrix_A - matrix_B):"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": false,
    "tags": [
     "nbsphinx-thumbnail"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": "<Figure size 1133.86x794.551 with 18 Axes>",
      "image/png": "\n"
     },
     "execution_count": 4,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "frame = XAxis() + \\\n",
    "    Cool(cl1, style=\"window\") + \\\n",
    "    Cool(cl2) + \\\n",
    "    HiCDiff(cl1, cl2, normalize='expect', diff_method='diff', cmap=\"bwr_r\") + \\\n",
    "    MinValue(-6) + MaxValue(6)  + \\\n",
    "    XAxis()\n",
    "frame *= Feature(depth_ratio=0.35)\n",
    "frame.plot(region)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### CLI code"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%bash\n",
    "\n",
    "data_dir=\"../../../tests/test_data/\"\n",
    "cl1=\"${data_dir}/cool_chr1_89000000_90400000_for_cmp_1.mcool\"\n",
    "cl2=\"${data_dir}/cool_chr1_89000000_90400000_for_cmp_2.mcool\"\n",
    "\n",
    "coolbox add XAxis - \\\n",
    "start_with Feature --depth_ratio \"0.35\" - \\\n",
    "    add Cool $cl1 - \\\n",
    "    add Cool $cl2 - \\\n",
    "    add HiCDiff $cl1 $cl2 --normalize 'expect' --diff_method 'diff' --cmap 'bwr_r' - \\\n",
    "    add MinValue \"-6\" - \\\n",
    "    add MaxValue \"6\" - \\\n",
    "end_with - \\\n",
    "add XAxis - \\\n",
    "goto \"chr1:89237500-90227500\" - \\\n",
    "plot /tmp/test_coolbox.png"
   ]
  }
 ],
